Package: minirextendr
Title: Scaffold miniextendr R Packages
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    c(
        person("Mossa M.", "Reimert", , "mossa@sund.ku.dk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("A2-AI", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: Utility functions for creating and maintaining R packages
    that use miniextendr for Rust integration. Similar to usethis but
    specialized for the miniextendr framework. Provides scaffolding
    templates, workflow helpers, and GitHub-based vendoring of miniextendr
    crates.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/CGMossa/miniextendr
BugReports: https://github.com/CGMossa/miniextendr/issues
